## Current Project State (snapshot)

- **Complete:** SQLite + FTS5 storage, sqlite-vec ANN search (`chunks_vec` vec0
  table, 768-dim cosine, `search_chunks_semantic`), `LemonadeProvider` embeddings,
  hardware abstraction (`src/hardware/`), unified inference queue
  (`src/inference_queue.rs`), `LemonadeRerankProvider` + `InferenceQueue::rerank()`,
  `cli_demo` FTS5 + semantic search + rerank pipeline, all 9 tracked bugs resolved.
- **New in this session:** `src/search.rs` — `search_hybrid()` free async function,
  `HybridSearchConfig`, `HybridSearchResult`, `SearchSources`; Reciprocal Rank
  Fusion (RRF, k=60) merge of FTS5 + sqlite-vec ANN results; optional cross-encoder
  rerank stage; `fts5_sanitize()` helper that strips FTS5-illegal punctuation from
  natural-language queries before the SQLite MATCH call; graceful degradation at
  every AI stage (no-embedding → FTS-only, no-reranker → RRF scores); 27 unit tests
  (all passing, no server required); `cli_demo` 🔀 hybrid search demo with per-query
  provenance labels (`[FTS]`, `[SEM]`, `[FTS+SEM+RR]`) and an alpha-sweep comparison.
- **Remaining:** axum HTTP server (Phase 3), streaming LLM responses (Phase 4
  remainder), Cargo workspace split (Phase 5).
- **No active bugs.** Do not reference BUG-1 through BUG-9 as open issues.

